des:
Ask for Yoga Facts, and learn about what truly matters in life.

Yoga Facts provides fun the entire shared flat - some of the quotes are as a joke so don't take it too seriously.

To start, just say "Alexa, open Yoga Facts" or "Alexa, launch Yoga Facts" to get a fact.

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
